title: Intervention S01E09 - Cristine and Kelly P.
description:
Hello, there, Cristine! It's a lonely life balancing a job, alcoholism, and a baby boy. But she somehow manages to keep on chugging, literally. Whether it be on the train, outside of her work, or on her stoop, you can almost guarantee that she's holding a 32 oz. beer in a brown paper bag.
And then dear, sweet DJ Kelly P. A single mother, she and her adorable daughter seem quite close. But, Kelly's eating habits seem to be threatening to transfer over to her daughter. Anorexia is no joke; it becomes scarier when a six year old starts exhibiting the signs.
A great episode of Intervention with two ladies in trouble. Season 1, Episode 9.
